{"type": "article", "id": 7943, "title": "Berta Julià Sala 可以扭动的容器", "description": "", "date": "2015-03-31T07:19:09Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 3, "praise_count": 40, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605234507zSh0mEIHYfFPwOn2.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t西班牙设计师 Berta Julià Sala 设计的这套作品油 5 个食物容器组成，特别的是，这些容器可以被“捏”成任何一样东西的样子，杯子，罐子，碟子，碗等等。举个例子来说，我们用大碗洗完水果，只需要捏住碗口，就可以在食物不落下来的情况下把水倒干——相信现在大部分人的做法是用手挡住吧。他们甚至还能被封住口，作为存储空间使用。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605234503k3KMOvwz4jsn2Ryl.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606052345036wcW80vbisjQRaOJ.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605234504b3xBEKWZ2g1AaFy8.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"1.19559902\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605234505xhdzsVTMpODmlyq8.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605234505fSIhwZXuk4LiHDP2.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.66748166\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606052345059D8ego